spell_list.description: This ability grants the warlock an innate ability to infect their enemies with a dormant disease with every hostile spell. Dark Incubation has a 5% chance to trigger and lasts for 12 seconds. Once the target is infected, the warlock will be able to cast Dark Aggravation, dealing substantial damage to the target and surrounding enemies.

effect_list.description: Removes Dark Incubation from the caster.
Inflicts 88 - 131 disease damage on targets in Area of Effect
You must be maintaining Dark Incubation.
